data.description: Spacious and beautiful designed, this wonderful home is perfect for families who love to entertain or relax in comfort.  Feauturing 3 bedroom, 2 bathrooms, with a total of 1661 sq feet of living space, there's plenty of room for everyone to enjoy.  This stunning kitchen is equipped with all white appliances, a covenient dining area that opens up to the kitchen and an inviting living room with plenty of natural light.  This home presents a a fantastic opportunity to enjoy a peaceful community.  Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to make this your dream home.
